pdated in the last 5 minutes. Both sessions show recent update times, but they're both cron sessions, not user conversations.\\n\\n\\nThe cron job session from 17:03 has context tokens indicating it processed content, but that's just the job itself responding to the cron trigger. I need to check for actual user sessions like agent:main or those with the feishu channel to find real user activity.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_h0roz0nzyoe8_1\",\n              \"name\": \"sessions_list\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"activeMinutes\": 5,\n                \"messageLimit\": 1\n              }\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_h0roz0nzyoe8_2\",\n              \"name\": \"sessions_list\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"limit\": 10,\n                \"messageLimit\": 1\n              }\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774645506749\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:99dd3c6e-f440-4ce5-a3aa-579918ee141b\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 服务状态巡检\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Cron: 服务状态巡检\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774645290833,\n      \"sessionId\": \"02c030ae-d15b-4f4f-b1ac-2edab42f0736\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 45081,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/02c030ae-d15b-4f4f-b1ac-2edab42f0736.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n 